      • primaryInstitutionName

        public java.lang.String primaryInstitutionName()
        Returns the primary institution name. This method will try to return a primary School in case the user is a student.

      • primaryOccupationName

        public java.lang.String primaryOccupationName()
        Returns the user primary occupation. This method will also check the users education fields if the user is a student.

      • isPremium

        public boolean isPremium()
        Returns true if the user is premium, otherwise false. The assumption on which this method is based, is that each premium user has at least one premium service enabled.

      • isBlacklisted

        public boolean isBlacklisted()
        Returns true if the user is blacklisted, otherwise false. The assumption on which this method is based, is that the XING API will always return a user id if the user is not blocked or blacklisted.
